olution and problem-solving abilities. Administrative and supervisory experience. Commitment to patron service and community engagement. Hourly Rate: The Hourly Rate for this position ranges from $25.00 to $30.00 per hour depending on qualifications and experience. Average week is 30 hours. How to Apply Interested candidates are invited to submit their resume and cover letter via email to braunwyn@citywest.ca on or before November 15, 2024. A detailed Job Description is available on our website: https://hazelton.bc.libraries.coop/library-information/job-opportunities/library-director-chief-librarian-position/ We thank all applicants for their interest; however, only short-listed applicants will be contacted. Compensation $25.00 to $30.00 per hour Closes: 15 November, 2024 Hazelton District Public Library Hazelton , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
